# ğŸš€ CodeFabric: AI Code Generation Package

Welcome to CodeFabric, your AI-powered coding assistant that generates projects faster than you can say "pip install"! ğŸš€ Feed it your project idea, and itâ€™ll craft code like a digital artisan ğŸ§™â€â™‚ï¸. Powered by LangGraph, itâ€™s automation with a touch of brilliance âœ¨.

